2. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence): The paper uses deep learning models for time series classification and proposes a new distance measurement. 
3. cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms): The paper deals with time series classification and proposes a new distance measurement. 
4. cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing): The paper uses LSTM neural network for time series classification. 
5. cs.SY (Systems and Control): The paper deals with energy consumption monitoring and analysis in data centers, which falls under the domain of systems and control.
